The following construct is not supported:

```
parameter condition = 1'b0;

typedef struct packed {
    logic [31:0] data;
} data_t;

data_t dt;

assign dt = condition ? 32'b0 : '{data:32'hf};  // error here

```

Got error: "Assignment pattern member not underneath a supported construct: COND".
